data.description: Discover the potential, a perfect blend of comfort and opportunity in this versatile property. Boasting commercial zoning and large shop with unfinished office space and RV parking with power/water, this property is ideal for both living and business ventures.  Inside a spacious kitchen and living area plus an extra large secondary bedroom offer ample room to relax and entertain. Outside, mature fruit trees and blueberries adorn the fenced landscape, while abundant parking and storage, a detached boathouse,  private well and included appliances ensure convenience and self-sufficiency. Don't miss out - seize a chance to own a property ready for whatever the future holds.
